Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}ここは…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}誰か
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:27.92,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}誰か
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:28.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}助けて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}誰か
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:34.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あーら、お姉様
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:36.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,もうお目覚めだったのね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.77,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ご機嫌はいかが?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.52,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&335580\4c&335580}いい夢は見られたかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.87,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&2D5680\4c&2D5680}もっと急いでください
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:26.63,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そう焦っても状況は変わらん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,少しは落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,随分冷静なんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.88,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あなたの婚約者が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.51,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,今どんな目に遭っているかも分からないというのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,本当に間違いないのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:41.64,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:42.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,美世は斎森にいるはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}美世は斎森にいるはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:48.40,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}なかなかお目覚めにならないから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:52.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}ついに心の臓が止まってしまわれたのかと思ってしまったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:57.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ど…どういうつもりで、こんなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,本当にいまいましい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あなたはおとなしく使用人をしているか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どこぞで野たれ死んでいればよかったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.33,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,この身の程知らずが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:13.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あなた、久堂様の婚約者から今すぐ降りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:15.97,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いいこと?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,久堂様にあなたの口から
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:20.89,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,「縁談をお断りします」って言うのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:27.77,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,やっぱり、お姉様に久堂様の妻は荷が重すぎると思うのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:36.74,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そんなきれいなお着物なんか身に着けちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:39.45,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,分不相応だとは思わないの?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:45.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,断るって約束してくれないかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,でないと、この大事な大事なお着物を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お姉様に似合うように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,仕立て直さなきゃいけなくなってしまうわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.64,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,こーんなに高価な着物を買ってもらうお願いができるんだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:11.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,縁談をなかったことにするのも簡単でしょう?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.23,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私が久堂様と婚約したら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お姉様には幸次さんを返してあげるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,さあ、お姉様
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,久堂様には何て言うのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,や…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:26.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,や?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.66,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,イヤーッ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.67,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1450,1057)\bord0\shad0}違うでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.68,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私が聞きたいのは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}そんな言葉じゃないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:52.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと、お姉様の口から聞かせてちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:56.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,「縁談を断る」って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.69,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.74,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうしてこんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:07.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ここで諦めてしまうのはきっと簡単
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,でも、これだけは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.33,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,これだけは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,誰にも譲りたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうしたの?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,声が出ないの?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.47,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お姉様は本当に駄目ね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:31.85,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,…ヤです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.73,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,イヤです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.73,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そんなお願いは聞けません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:42.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,生意気な!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:47.99,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,この
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:48.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お母様
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私に任せて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:01.97,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お姉様はやっぱり地べたがお似合いね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.97,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.10,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お姉様は出来損ないでしょ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.10,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私と違って見鬼の才もなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.85,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,長所の1つもないじゃない?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.27,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そんな家の恥のお姉様が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.52,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,久堂様の妻になんて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,初めからどうかしていたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1360,1057)\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}おい、開けろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.49,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}いいと思わない?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}この斎森のおうちも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:30.58,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,幸次さんも手に入るのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:35.54,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お姉様はそれをずっと望んでいたでしょう?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.46,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私が…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,旦那様の…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,久堂清霞の婚約者です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.89,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,絶対に譲れません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何よ、それ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.81,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いいかげんにおし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:00.44,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,その年まで、育ててやった恩を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:05.45,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,嫁に行った途端に、あだで返そうだなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,本当にいやらしい子ね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あなたなんかに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:15.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,わたくしの人生が狂わされてたまるものかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}今までの私なら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:21.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}きっと謝っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}早く嵐が去るように
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.76,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}そうやって生きてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:30.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}そのほうが楽だったから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:35.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}でも、諦めたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:36.98,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:40.61,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}何もできなかった昔の私とは違う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:42.32,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.07,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}旦那様の元へ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.15,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,おい、少し下がってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.32,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,なんて諦めの悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.33,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}なんてことを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:08.59,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,く…久堂殿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,待ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.22,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,これは一体?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.81,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}美世はどこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.85,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}斎森殿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.48,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,美世?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,美世ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.73,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,もう久堂家には戻らぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.40,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,父さん、あなたって人は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,久堂清霞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}これほど早く来ようとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}私の婚約者はどこにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.87,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}美世はもうあなたには会わぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}戻らぬと言っている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.63,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,本人の意思は本人に聞いて確かめる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,言わないなら、そこをどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}断る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}無理にでも通るというのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.14,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}こちらとて黙ってはおれん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.47,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ならば力ずくで押し通る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.60,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ま…待たれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.69,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,一体どうなっている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:02.69,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,辰石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:05.15,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あとで娘に話を聞くことだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,正門は木っ端みじんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.74,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,このまま侵入を許せば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,この屋敷も破壊されかねんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.58,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}それがイヤなら、お前も手を貸せ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,さすがは久堂家の当主だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,無駄なことを
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.45,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,本物の化け物か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.33,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3a&88}邪魔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:04.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&804A46\4c&804A46\3a&88}どけ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,戦いにすらならない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.27,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&406480\4c&406480\3a&44}大人と赤子ほどの実力差だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:25.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&406480\4c&406480\3a&44}これが…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:30.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,当代最強と言われる異能者の実力なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.49,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何なの？今の
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,み…見苦しいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.59,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,早く言いなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.30,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,「久堂家との縁談をお断りします」と
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.68,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,イヤです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.43,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,この
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:08.44,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いいかげん、立場をわきまえろと言っているのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,もう、決して譲らない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私を信じてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,旦那様のために
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&406780\4c&406780\3a&44}美世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:22.83,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,蔵?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,今はほとんど使われていない古い蔵があります
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,もしかしたら、美世はそこに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,案内しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:33.25,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.65,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D3580\4c&0D3580}行かせるかーっ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:51.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D3580\4c&0D3580}父さん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D3580\4c&0D3580}こんな所で炎を使うとは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.15,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D3580\4c&0D3580}どこまで愚かになれば気が済む
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.92,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D3580\4c&0D3580}なんてことを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:18.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&337C80\4c&337C80\3a&44}美世は渡さん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:19.93,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&4C7099\4c&4C7099\3a&66}そこまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.45,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,気絶させただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:40.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,急ぐぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&03195C\4c&03195C}なぜこんなことに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}いいかげんに言いなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}「縁談を断る」って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.13,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}早く
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}以前の私は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}命が尽きる瞬間を待っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:14.52,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}毎日が苦しくて、悲しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:18.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}心を殺したまま、生きるのにも疲れて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:21.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\3a&66}自分の居場所なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\3a&66}どこにもないと思っていたから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.99,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}違った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:37.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\an8\3c&627280\4c&627280\3a&66}私がお前にここにいてほしいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.76,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\3c&627280\4c&627280\3a&66}居場所はあった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:44.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,2000)}あの人のそばに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}言え、早く!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:52.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}絶対に…言いま…せん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:56.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}言えーっ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:03.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}私は…旦那様のおそばに…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,久堂様?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&284980\4c&284980}美世
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,本当に来てくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.14,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:40.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}私、諦めませんでしたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.49,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,美世
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.83,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,旦那様…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,もう、大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私なんかのために
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,こんな所まで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.14,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ありがとうござい…ます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,さっきから、一体何の…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そんな…イヤ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,イヤーッ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:44.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,こんなふうになるまで、何をした?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:50.51,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,無抵抗の人間にこれほどの傷を負わせてまで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.81,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何をさせようとした?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:57.06,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私は悪くありませんわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:00.31,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私はただ、間違いを正そうと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:02.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そう思っただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,間違い?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.40,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お姉様は見鬼の才はないし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.03,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,見た目も貧相で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.99,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,使用人としても使えない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:15.16,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そんな人が久堂家に受け入れてもらえるだなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.08,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何かの間違いでしょう?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:22.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お父様もお母様も、私を一番だと言ってくれるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お姉様と大違いだって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.67,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,すべてにおいて、私のほうが…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.34,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:33.26,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,これ以上、お前のたわ言は聞きたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.48,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.61,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうして分かってくださらないの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.36,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ひどいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お前のくだらん自慢話はもうたくさんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:56.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私がお前のような傲慢な女を選ぶことなど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:59.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,天地がひっくり返ってもありえん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:00.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どけ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:16.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.89,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうしてこうなるの?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.10,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,香耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.40,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,僕たちも避難しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私は間違ってないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.32,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,離して
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.07,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ねえ、放っておいて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:31.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,うるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.16,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,何よ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,幸次さんはお姉様が好きなんでしょう?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,私のことなんて構わずに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:42.21,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,さっさと逃げればいいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ああ、そうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:45.75,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,君の言うとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.13,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,僕が一番大事なのは美世だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.63,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,でもね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.14,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,君なんかでも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.30,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,死んだら美世は悲しむ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:59.31,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,また傷を増やすことになるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:00.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,君の…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.14,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いや、僕たちのせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:04.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,だから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.32,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,絶対に置いていくもんか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:29.59,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&99768A\4c&99768A\3a&88}大きくなったわね、美世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&99768A\4c&99768A}お母様
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:39.43,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&B2968F\4c&B2968F\3a&88}いろいろと、つらい思いをさせてしまって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.22,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&B2968F\4c&B2968F\3a&88}ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:45.64,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(460,1057)\3a&88}自分を信じるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:48.48,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(460,1057)\3a&aa}あなたの中のその力を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3a&aa}私の…力?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:08.88,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,いとわしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.25,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,憎らしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:14.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&456980\4c&456980}ほんに目障りなことよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,辰石の役立たずめ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,このままでは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,薄刃の血は久堂のものではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:30.77,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,そろそろ、例の許可を賜りたく存じます
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:36.03,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,どうか、我々に悲願成就の機会をお与えください
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:39.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,あるべきものを、あるべき場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,近く状況は動く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,行動を許可しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:51.04,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ただし、時機を見誤らぬことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,かしこまりました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&446C80\4c&446C80}では、予定どおり
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.76,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}行動を開始させていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:05.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}必ずや、あの異能は潰すのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,旦那様?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:34.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,美世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&44}旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.34,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&44}ああ、私だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&44}無理をするな、寝ていろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.10,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&44}あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:45.56,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&44}でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.03,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}本当に大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:00.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:01.66,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:03.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.83,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}今回は、私の不注意のせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:07.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}お前のせいではない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}お前のせいではない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}決して、何ひとつ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:15.75,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,お前は悪くないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.64,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.14,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}美世様
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:36.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,ゆり江さん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:39.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}美世様
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:41.28,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:43.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}意識が戻られて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:46.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}ゆり江さん、あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}顔を上げてください
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:51.00,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}もし美世様に何かあったらと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:52.67,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}ゆり江は…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:54.67,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}ゆり江は…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:03.05,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&805839\4c&805839\3a&44}本当に、美世が無事でよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:09.68,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&88}はい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}這裡是…
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}有人嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.76,0:00:27.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}有人嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.92,0:00:28.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}救救我
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}有人嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.55,0:00:34.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,哎呀，姊姊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.39,0:00:36.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您醒了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.77,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,感覺如何?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.52,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&335580\4c&335580}做美夢了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&2D5680\4c&2D5680}請您再快一點
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.33,0:02:26.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你再著急也於事無補
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您倒是冷靜
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.88,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,但您的未婚妻
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不知道已經吃了多少苦頭了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你確定沒搞錯嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.97,0:02:41.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.02,0:02:42.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世一定在齋森家
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}美世一定在齋森家
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.81,0:02:48.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}看您遲遲不醒
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.40,0:02:52.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我還以為您的心臟停止跳動了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.15,0:02:57.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,為…為什麼要這樣對我
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,真是令人厭惡
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳為什麼不好好做傭人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,或者乾脆死在什麼地方
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,真是不知死活
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.58,0:03:13.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳必須立刻和久堂大人解除婚約
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.76,0:03:15.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳要親口對他說
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.18,0:03:20.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,「我要和您解除婚約」
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.76,0:03:27.77,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,對姊姊來說，做久堂大人的妻子過於辛苦了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.90,0:03:36.74,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,身穿如此華美的和服
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.99,0:03:39.45,Dial-CHI,？,0,0,0,,您覺得自己有這個資格嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.62,0:03:45.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您會答應回絕這樁婚事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不然，您這件漂亮的和服
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,就會被我親手
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,裁剪得和您一樣不堪入目
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,這麼昂貴的和服，您都能讓他賣給您
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.68,0:04:11.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,解除婚約想必不是問題吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.23,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我和久堂大人定親後
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,就會把幸次先生還給您
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,好了，姊姊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您會對久堂大人說什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,住…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.04,0:04:26.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,住?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.66,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}住手
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1450,1004)\bord0\shad0}不對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.68,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我想聽的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}不是這句話
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.89,0:04:52.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,請姊姊務必親口說
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.19,0:04:56.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,「我要解除婚約」
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.74,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.41,0:05:07.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,在這裡放棄一定很簡單
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,可唯獨這件事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,唯獨這件事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不願向任何人讓步
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不出聲嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,姊姊未免太沒用了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.73,0:05:31.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,…不要
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不會提出那種請求
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.15,0:05:42.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳放肆!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.58,0:05:47.99,Dial-CHI,？,0,0,0,,死丫頭
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.99,0:05:48.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,母親
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.59,0:06:01.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,姊姊還是適合躺在地上
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您知道自己一無是處嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您不光沒有我的見鬼之才
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,甚至沒有任何長處
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,讓家族蒙羞的姊姊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.52,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,做久堂大人的妻子
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,簡直再荒唐不過了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1360,1004)\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}喂，開門
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}您不覺得很划算嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}不僅能留在齋森家
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.66,0:06:30.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,還能得到幸次先生
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.75,0:06:35.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,這不是您一直盼望的事嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.46,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.55,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,老爺的…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,久堂清霞的未婚妻
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我絕不讓步
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳給我住口
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.94,0:07:00.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,這麼多年，我把妳養大
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.78,0:07:05.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,出閣沒多久，就對我反咬一口
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,真是豈有此理
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳這小丫頭
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.79,0:07:15.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,休想毀掉我的人生
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}若是以前的我
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.42,0:07:21.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}肯定會開口求饒
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}讓風暴早點結束
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}然後繼續苟活
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.76,0:07:30.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}畢竟這樣比較輕鬆
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.35,0:07:35.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}可是，我不想放棄
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.56,0:07:36.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}我已經…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.98,0:07:40.61,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}不是過去那個一無是處的我了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.61,0:07:42.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}我要…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}回到老爺身邊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,喂，你退後一些
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,竟然如此難纏
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}太驚人了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.55,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.92,0:08:08.59,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,久…久堂閣下
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,且慢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}美世在哪裡
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}齋森閣下
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.48,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世她
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不會再回久堂家了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,父親，你太過分了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,久堂清霞
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}沒想到你來得這麼快
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}我的未婚妻在哪裡
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}美世已經不想見你了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}也不會再回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,這些話，我自會向她確認
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不想回答就給我閃開
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}我拒絕
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}你要是打算硬闖
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}我可不會無動於衷
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那我只能強行闖入了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.60,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,且…且慢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.69,0:09:02.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,辰石
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.69,0:09:05.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,事後問你女兒吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,大門已經化為齏粉了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.74,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,若是任其闖入
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,這座府邸必然不保
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&305F80\4c&305F80}你若是不願，就來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不愧是久堂家的家主
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,白費力氣
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,他當真是怪物嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3a&88}礙事
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.21,0:10:04.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&804A46\4c&804A46\3a&88}閃開
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,完全不是對手
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&406480\4c&406480\3a&44}實力差距可謂天壤之別
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.81,0:10:25.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&406480\4c&406480\3a&44}這就是…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.31,0:10:30.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,當代最強異能者的實力嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,真…真是礙眼
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.59,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,快跟我說
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,「我要和久堂家解除婚約」
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.68,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,死丫頭
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.56,0:11:08.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳最好知道什麼叫自知之明
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我絕對不會讓步
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不能辜負
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,老爺的信任
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&406780\4c&406780\3a&44}美世
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.08,0:11:22.83,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,倉房?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,有一間老倉房，如今幾乎廢棄了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世很可能就在那裡
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,帶路
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.59,0:11:33.25,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D3580\4c&0D3580}你休想過去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.86,0:11:51.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D3580\4c&0D3580}父親
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D3580\4c&0D3580}竟然在這種地方馭火
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D3580\4c&0D3580}你真是愚不可及
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D3580\4c&0D3580}怎會如此
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.01,0:12:18.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&337C80\4c&337C80\3a&44}你休想帶走美世
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.13,0:12:19.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&4C7099\4c&4C7099\3a&66}到此為止了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,只是讓他昏了過去
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.24,0:12:40.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&03195C\4c&03195C}為何會落到這步田地
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}快跟我說
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}「我要解除婚約」
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}快說
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}以前的我
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只會靜靜地等待命數告終
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.39,0:13:14.52,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}日日愁苦，夜夜傷悲
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.52,0:13:18.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}猶如行屍走肉，沒有任何指望
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.07,0:13:21.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\3a&66}認為這世上
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\3a&66}根本沒有自己的容身之處
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.99,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我錯了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.42,0:13:37.55,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\an8\3c&627280\4c&627280\3a&66}我希望妳留在這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\3c&627280\4c&627280\3a&66}我找到歸宿了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.26,0:13:44.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,2000)}就在他身邊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}快跟我說!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.68,0:13:52.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我絕對…不…說
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.02,0:13:56.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}跟我說!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.23,0:14:03.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我要回到老爺身邊去…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,久堂大人?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&284980\4c&284980}美世
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你真的來了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,老爺
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.94,0:14:40.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我沒有放棄
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.83,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,老爺…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,為了我這種人
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您竟然找到了這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,從剛才開始到底是…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.38,0:15:44.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳們對她做了什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.09,0:15:50.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,竟然讓把一個普通人折磨成這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳們想讓她做什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.31,0:15:57.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我沒有錯
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.35,0:16:00.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我只是想糾正錯誤
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.90,0:16:02.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,錯誤?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,姊姊沒有見鬼之才
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.03,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,相貌也是平平
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.99,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,連傭人都做不好
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.66,0:16:15.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,久堂家豈能收留她這種人
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.08,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,一定是哪裡搞錯了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.41,0:16:22.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,父親和母親都說，我才是最出色的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,和姊姊完全不同
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼看，我都比她…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.97,0:16:33.26,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不想再聽妳胡言亂語了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.48,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.61,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您為什麼不理解我呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,太過分了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我已經聽夠了妳的妄言妄語
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.95,0:16:56.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我絕不會選妳這種傲慢的女人
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.95,0:16:59.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,哪怕是天翻地覆
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.79,0:17:00.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,閃開
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.10,0:17:16.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,香耶
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我們也去避難吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我沒有錯
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我讓你別管我
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.07,0:17:31.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,幸次先生不是喜歡姊姊嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,那你還管我做什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.29,0:17:42.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,自己逃走不就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,對，沒錯
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.46,0:17:45.75,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,正如妳所言
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我最珍視的人是美世
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,即便妳這種人死了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世也會傷心流淚
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.22,0:17:59.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,又會在心底平添一道傷痕
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.93,0:18:00.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,因為妳…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不，因為我們的過錯
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.94,0:18:04.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不會對妳棄之不顧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.38,0:18:29.59,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&99768A\4c&99768A\3a&88}妳長大了呢，美世
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&99768A\4c&99768A}母親大人
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.22,0:18:39.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&B2968F\4c&B2968F\3a&88}讓妳經歷了許多苦難
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&B2968F\4c&B2968F\3a&88}對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.97,0:18:45.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\pos(460,1004)\3a&88}妳要相信自己
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.64,0:18:48.48,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\pos(460,1004)\3a&aa}相信自己體內的力量
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3a&aa}我的…力量?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.21,0:19:08.88,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,可憎啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.46,0:19:11.25,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,可恨啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.55,0:19:14.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&456980\4c&456980}實在是過於礙眼
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,辰石家的廢物
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,再這樣下去
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,薄刃之血就會歸久堂所有
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}陛下
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.60,0:19:30.77,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,此前一事，還請您恩准
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.40,0:19:36.03,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,請給予我等實現夙願的機會
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.95,0:19:39.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,使令萬象，各歸其位
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,風雲即將變幻
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,特允爾等行動
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.42,0:19:51.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不過，切不可貽誤時機
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&446C80\4c&446C80}我們將按照計劃
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}實施行動方案
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.60,0:20:05.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}務必擊潰那個異能
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,老爺?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.09,0:20:34.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.55,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&44}老爺
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&806666\4c&806666\3a&44}嗯，是我
